  <brief_title>A Study of Cabergoline for the Treatment of Cocaine Dependence - 1</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 2, Double-Blind, Placebo Controlled Trial of Cabergoline for the Treatment of Cocaine Dependence</official_title>
  <sponsors>
